The toolchains' commands for compilation contain only the relevant macro definitions at each stage. I.e. the assembler command contains only those macros necessary for assembly. 

This was intended to fix an issue with command buffer length for armasm within uvision. Many OOB testers were seeing the following error: https://github.com/project-generator/project_generator/issues/429.

